    "description_long": "This is a large, modern pickup truck with a four-door crew cab configuration and a short cargo bed at the rear. The body is predominantly white with black-tinted windows and a black bed cover, giving it a sleek, urban appearance. The front features a wide grille with horizontal slats and integrated headlights, while the rear has a tailgate and vertical taillights. The vehicle sits on five-spoke wheels with visible wheel arches and side steps for easier entry. Roof rails and a sunroof are present, adding to its utility and upscale look. The overall design suggests a robust yet refined vehicle suitable for both city and light off-road use.",
